Mike Ragan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_Ragan 0 Not related to the political activist Michael Reagan, adopted son of Ronald ReaganMike Ragan (born Hollis Alan Bane, February 18, 1918 - August 25, 1995), was an American actor of primarily western films and television—but some dramatic roles, too—from the 1940s until 1968.
